'''Domain Muyel''' was a [[Domain]] among the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. During their [[Yuuzhan Vong War|invasion]] of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], [[Supreme Overlord]] [[Shimrra Jamaane|Shimrra]] granted them stewardship of a whole star system. However, when [[Warmaster]] [[Nas Choka]] order them to send ships to help his armada destroy [[Zonama Sekot/Legends|Zonama Sekot]], Domain Muyel refused to send a single ship to the [[Coruscant system/Legends|Coruscant system]].<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

